highlights.text: “Extssy Model” by Junior H has been on Top Songs Mexico the longest, at 1037 days straight.
Fuerza Regida has the most spots on Top Songs Mexico. “TU SANCHO” is the highest at #3.
“Necesito Decirte” by Conjunto Primavera is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mexico at #189.
“Orula” by RZR is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mexico, up 57 spots at #86.
